title: Sassy Princess Is a Doctor - Novel Updates
tags: Ancient Times   Doctors   Female Protagonist   Transmigration   Ugly Protagonist   Ugly to Beautiful
author: 蚂蚁上树
description: 'You, come here for a hug.' 'I'm sorry, Your Highness, but you can't hug me as you like.' She holds a fresh-faced young man with her left hand and a lady killer with her right hand. How could she let him have her so easily? Let's see how the domineering and bossy prince wins the heart of this sassy girl with the unparalleled beauty.>
